#message on the initial WHOIS TOOL PAGE
<-WHOIS_TOOL_PAGE
<pre>
<strong>Current Input</strong>: none

Enter a valid domain name (<a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fully_qualified_domain_name' target='_blank'>FQDN</a>) / <a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IPv4' taget='_blank'>IPv4 Address</a>.


The '<a href='/cgi-bin/whois.zyx'>whois.zyx</a>' script on a nutshell:  

The <a class='tooltip' href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WHOIS#Software' target='_blank' >whois command<span class='tooltiptext'>On Unix-like operating systems, the whois command is a client for the WHOIS directory service.</span></a> is utilized by the script to perform a whois query at the known Registry whois server for the  <a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Top-level_domain' target='_blank' class='tooltip' >TLD<span class='tooltiptext' >Top Level Domain</span></a>. If a Registrar whois server is found on the result of the whois query done on the  Registry's whois server, the script will utilize the whois command again and will do the same query on the whois server of the Registrar. 

And for IP addresses, the script will utilize the whois command to perform a whois query to the appropriate <a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Regional_Internet_registry'  target='_blank' class='tooltip'>RIR<span class='tooltiptext'>Regional Internet Registry.</span></a> whois server.

If the input is a domain name, the script will present two tabs. The Registry tab contains the raw whois query result from the whois server of the Registry, this tab also contains the Registry whois server queried by the script.  If a registrar whois server is found, The Registrar tab shall contain the raw whois query result from the whois server of the Registrar, this tab also contains the Registrar whois server queried by the script.  If the input is an IP address the raw whois query result from the appropriate RIR will be displayed, the page will also contain the whois server queried by the script. 

It is also possible to specify a whois server and port for the query, by clicking the '<span style='color:tomato;'>+</span>' before the Who is button.
</pre>
WHOIS_TOOL_PAGE->

